SELECT q.quiz_name, COUNT(a.answer_id) AS num_answers FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id GROUP BY q.quiz_name HAVING num_answers > 10;

SELECT q.quiz_name, AVG(CAST(a.correct_answer AS INT)) AS avg_correct_answers FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.question_id JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id GROUP BY q.quiz_name HAVING avg_correct_answers > 0.75;

SELECT q.quiz_name, q.quiz_category, COUNT(DISTINCT qu.question_id) AS num_questions FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id GROUP BY q.quiz_name, q.quiz_category ORDER BY num_questions DESC;

SELECT q.quiz_name, q.quiz_category, SUM(CASE WHEN a.correct_answer THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS num_correct_answers, SUM(CASE WHEN NOT a.correct_answer THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS num_incorrect_answers FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id GROUP BY q.quiz_name, q.quiz_category;
SELECT q.quiz_id, q.quiz_name, COUNT(DISTINCT qu.question_id) AS num_questions FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id GROUP BY q.quiz_id, q.quiz_name HAVING num_questions >= 5;
SELECT q.quiz_name, COUNT(*) AS num_questions FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id GROUP BY q.quiz_name HAVING num_questions < 10;

SELECT q.quiz_name, q.quiz_category, COUNT(DISTINCT a.answer_id) AS num_answers FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id GROUP BY q.quiz_name, q.quiz_category HAVING num_answers > 20;

SELECT q.quiz_name, AVG(DATE_TRUNC('day', CURRENT_DATE) - DATE_TRUNC('day', a.created_at)) AS avg_response_time FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id WHERE a.correct_answer = TRUE GROUP BY q.quiz_name;

SELECT q.quiz_name, q.quiz_category, MAX(DATE_TRUNC('day', CURRENT_DATE) - DATE_TRUNC('day', a.created_at)) AS max_response_time FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id WHERE a.correct_answer = TRUE GROUP BY q.quiz_name, q.quiz_category;
SELECT q.quiz_name, COUNT(DISTINCT qu.question_id) AS num_questions FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id WHERE q.quiz_category = 'Programming' GROUP BY q.quiz_name;

SELECT q1.quiz_name AS quiz_name_1, q2.quiz_name AS quiz_name_2, COUNT(*) AS common_questions FROM quizzes q1 JOIN questions qu1 ON q1.quiz_id = qu1.quiz_id JOIN questions qu2 ON qu1.question_id = qu2.question_id JOIN quizzes q2 ON qu2.quiz_id = q2.quiz_id GROUP BY quiz_name_1, quiz_name_2;
SELECT q.quiz_name, COUNT(a.answer_id) AS num_answers FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id LEFT JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id GROUP BY q.quiz_name;

SELECT q.quiz_name, COUNT(*) AS num_questions FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id LEFT JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id WHERE a.answer_id IS NULL GROUP BY q.quiz_name HAVING num_questions > 0;

SELECT q.quiz_name AS quiz_name_1, COUNT(DISTINCT a1.answer_id) AS num_answers_1, COUNT(DISTINCT a2.answer_id) AS num_answers_2 FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu1 ON q.quiz_id = qu1.quiz_id JOIN answers a1 ON qu1.question_id = a1.question_id JOIN questions qu2 ON q.quiz_id = qu2.quiz_id JOIN answers a2 ON qu2.question_id = a2.question_id WHERE a1.answer_text = a2.answer_text AND a1.answer_id < a2.answer_id GROUP BY quiz_name_1 HAVING num_answers_1 = num_answers_2;

SELECT q.quiz_name, q.quiz_category, MAX(DATE_TRUNC('week', CURRENT_DATE) - DATE_TRUNC('week', a.created_at)) AS max_response_time FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.quiz_id JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id WHERE a.correct_answer = TRUE GROUP BY q.quiz_name, q.quiz_category;

SELECT q.quiz_name, AVG(a.correct_answer::INT) AS avg_correct_answers FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.question_id JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id GROUP BY q.quiz_name;

SELECT q.quiz_category, AVG(a.correct_answer::INT) AS avg_correct_answers FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.question_id JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id GROUP BY q.quiz_category HAVING AVG(a.correct_answer::INT) > 0.5;

SELECT q.quiz_name, AVG(CASE WHEN a.correct_answer THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS avg_correct_answers FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.question_id JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id GROUP BY q.quiz_name HAVING avg_correct_answers >= 0.75;

SELECT q.quiz_name, AVG(CASE WHEN a.correct_answer THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS avg_correct_answers FROM quizzes q JOIN questions qu ON q.quiz_id = qu.question_id JOIN answers a ON qu.question_id = a.question_id WHERE a.created_at BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' GROUP BY q.quiz_name HAVING avg_correct_answers <= 0.5;
